<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <p><em>This is an automated email message, please do not reply!</em></p>
    
    <h1>Dear VATEUD PTD Administrator,</h1>
    <p>
      A pilot has requested a theory exam token reissue for <%= @pilot.rating.name %> rating!<br/>
      
      Pilot details:<br /><br />

      Name: <%= @pilot.name %><br/>
      VATSIM ID: <%= @pilot.vatsimid %><br/>
      Email: <%= @pilot.email %><br/>
      Division: <%= @pilot.division.name %><br/>
      vACC: <%= @pilot.vacc %><br/>
      ATC rating: <%= @pilot.atc_rating.name %><br/>
    </p>
    <p>
      After reissuing the token in ATSimTest, you can manage his record and
      mark the "token reissued" checkbox in the pilot's profile
      at <a href="http://ptd.vateud.net/admin">ptd.vateud.net/admin</a>. <br />
      The pilot will be notified when the token is reissued.
    </p>
    <p>Have a great day!</p>
    <p><em><strong>VATEUD Pilot Training Department Team</strong></em></p>
  </body>
</html>